{"type": "article", "id": 27240, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-24T06:49:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28038, "name": "Earth Stone Wood"}, {"id": 28039, "name": "The Whole Elements"}, {"id": 28040, "name": "Inupathy"}, {"id": 28041, "name": "Spendwallet"}, {"id": 28042, "name": "X Lab"}, {"id": 28043, "name": "One Piece Knife"}, {"id": 28044, "name": "Johanna Gauder"}, {"id": 22978, "name": "OBI"}, {"id": 28045, "name": "The Creative Method"}, {"id": 28046, "name": "lupo"}, {"id": 28047, "name": "bonpart"}, {"id": 28048, "name": "Anna Bera"}, {"id": 28049, "name": "Joji Yamaguchi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134125yL3S94YmIMhrGtWd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Earth Stone Wood by The Whole Elements</h2>\n<p>在家里放上巨石会是怎样一种景象？在设计师 Anna Bera 的构想中，它们不仅没有那么冷冰冰，反而营造出了极简的美感。最近她所创立的工作室 <a href=\"http://www.thewholeelements.com/\">The Whole Elements</a> 就推出了能够以假乱真的模块型木质家具 <a href=\"http://www.thewholeelements.com/#!esw/h0b8m\">Earth Stone Wood</a>，这些不规则的家具可以独立当作桌椅使用，也可以经过组合变成一个橱柜。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103745AzHv958VLQDcsXNw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103746rt05b7JQo1sWkCK6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103746wqzbeHcvElOmgDka.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103746MJFCc149npawoBRr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103747EtXAcmgCeBIhRwNZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103747stSpPWwC3l5rgvdx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Inupathy by Joji Yamaguchi</h2>\n<p>由于我们并不能通过语言直接同汪星人交流，要了解它们的内心世界不是件容易的事情。日本的软件工程师 Joji Yamaguchi 为此设计了一款可以视觉化汪星人心情的束带装置 <a href=\"http://inupathy.com/\">Inupathy</a>，它通过内置的心率传感器来检测狗狗的心跳，以此分析出狗狗的心情并通过 LED 灯的颜色变化反映出来。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103748G8xDJSFCBsp57Ony.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103748tgEeFR5MwmCdZsxj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103749PhQKRVTjnEaF8HmG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103749bOCIUjaHxNdzPSe2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103749uv8GdIRYrHaqhCmD.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Spendwallet by X Lab</h2>\n<p>付款并不支持移动支付？带多张银行卡太麻烦？X Lab 最近推出的一款电子钱包 Spendwallet 希望替你解决这两个烦恼：通过配套的读卡器和手机应用可以把银行卡的信息导入电子钱包中，最多可以存入 20 张卡。采用 X Lab 自行研发的仿磁场技术（Magnetic Flux Emulation），Spendwallet 还免去了“刷”这一动作，只需要贴近刷卡机就能完成支付。目前 Spendwallet 还在<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/spendwallet-no-more-cards-in-your-wallet--3#/\">进行众筹</a>，最低价为 99 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103751EnjL6gOlINJQRXut.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66720779\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103751kS3fiJWp4ntDEvgQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87438825\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103752xSKvGtUmVMjs3zbe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21451613\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021037523L1TgibUmW45nZuB.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103754fuXrRVHOhw3t4Z1T.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103755ZgaPW3yG9rkEFteb.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>One Piece Knife by Johanna Gauder</h2>\n<p>不同于市面上千篇一律的刀，德国设计师 Johanna Gauder 制作的这款 <a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/johannagauder/KNIFE\">One Piece Knife</a> 或许更适合用“艺术品”来形容：它由整块不锈钢制成，看起来就好像是一张微微翘起的白纸。一端经过弯曲形成刀柄，既简洁又美观。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103757gENJiAKlobD2QetL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.433\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103757GSkXYI7qhteM3ZbE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103758FX3zeOBd4PRgYI6w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Obi by The Creative Method</h2>\n<p>一到夏天，汽水总是必不可少的消暑饮料。由于越来越多的人开始注意健康，<a href=\"http://thecreativemethod.com/\">The Creative Method</a> 为 Obi 的益生菌汽水设计包装时选择强调“有益的气泡”这一概念。每款汽水都根据不同的风味印有由大小不一的气泡组成的水果，表现出了汽水清新的口感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103758yhlvw1sepRYNDzKu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103759vxKbRoqBuCpTcUh0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.145\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103759QcTCaoAGSbEW8x1k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.145\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103759W9moRiY6vbh8QdZX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>lupo by bonpart</h2>\n<p>如果你想要一盏“爱玩儿”的台灯，维也纳的双人设计组合 <a href=\"http://www.bonpart.at/\">bonpart</a> 推出的 <a href=\"http://www.bonpart.at/bonpart---lupo.html\">lupo</a> 会让你眼前一亮。它的造型可以说是极其简洁，仅由框架和折叠的金属灯罩组成。尽管简单，bonpart 并不想让它过于单调，两片灯罩都可以独立转动，营造出各式各样的光影效果。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103800LSOjClnypWVamQ7e.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103800xQLNChlgV5WBEtbw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.28239609\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103801z4DPX2FqowLSrRhJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103801JfTqhMYSsI8HNyz3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.44621027\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103802kTdIKPQH9j73RXSr.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70285714\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}